By Christopher Watson

Whoa! What Came Out of Seinfeld's Mouth Will Utterly Disgust You
Monday, January 15, 2018 15:25
 
None of us should be surprised about the disgusting things coming out of Hollywood.  Harvey Weinstein is a disgusting sexual predator, Kevin Spacey preys on kids, Matt Lauer is a hypocritical pervert and the list goes on and on.  There’s no telling how deep that cesspool really is.
What you’re about to see was sent to me by someone from facebook. Its a clip from a web series that has been streamed nearly 100 million times called Comedians in Cars Getting Coffee.
Its directed and hosted by comedian Jerry Seinfeld, distributed for the first nine seasons by the digital network Crackle, then moving to Netflix for season ten (2018). The series premiered on July 19, 2012.
Episodes feature Seinfeld introducing a vintage car selected for a guest comedian, followed by a drive to a preselected café or restaurant for coffee.
